        <li class="list-group-item">🔐 Secure role-based login (Faculty, HOI, Admin)</li>
        <li class="list-group-item">📚 Manage patents, publications, projects, events, book chapters, and awards</li>
        <li class="list-group-item">🗓 Filter by All Time, Yearly, Half-Yearly, Quarterly, Monthly</li>
        <li class="list-group-item">📊 Export detailed and summary reports in Excel format</li>
        <li class="list-group-item">🏫 HOI view: full school, departments, or individual faculty</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

